  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Postpartum Care Plan - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_postpartum_care_plan">Postpartum Care Plan</xref>
 is a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_plan">CARE PLAN</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_postpartum_care_plan">Postpartum Care Plan</xref>
 is a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_plan">CARE PLAN</xref>
 developed within a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_maternity_episode">Maternity Episode</xref>
 for the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_postpartum">Postpartum</xref>
 period.        </p>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_postpartum_care_plan">Postpartum Care Plan</xref>
 should include:        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>relevant details of medical history</p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
the 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONALS</xref>
 involved and their 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional_role">CARE PROFESSIONAL ROLES</xref>
               </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>feeding plans for the baby</p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
advice and management at each 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_contact">CARE CONTACT</xref>
 and                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>details of the mother's emotional well-being.</p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p> </p>
  </div>
